Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.28,1:44:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll end up with, well, we pretty much covered this subject, 39. We don't need
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.98,1:44:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the slides. So what we've defined now is a way of discerning truth from falsehood for
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.98,1:45:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time in human history. We have differentiated between the content of the field, the proximate
Dialogue: 0,1:45:05.39,1:45:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,context, that is, the conditions, the time, prevailing elements and influences, and
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.15,1:45:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,contrasted that with the absolute. We saw the consciousness calibration gives us, for
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.22,1:45:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time, a new tool for survival, for understanding, for spiritual growth and development.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.99,1:45:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Consequently, we are really a very fortunate generation. Mankind has never had the capacity
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.28,1:45:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell truth from falsehood. Therefore, he was fated to endless misery, war, all the
