Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.85,1:45:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All came out of not knowing truth from falsehood. Not knowing truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.09,1:46:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth arises then at, or our awareness of truth arises as a consequence of intention.
