Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.58,1:47:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is very often quite some disparity with the essential truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.58,1:47:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The book and the contents are not one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.09,1:47:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The media, of course, exploit that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:25.09,1:47:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of the biggest sources of disinformation and lack of integrity is the media, the media.
