Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.40,1:48:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That which desecrates beauty, then, tells you that is not the way you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.40,1:48:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Because beauty is one aspect of the sacred.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.23,1:49:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The attributes of God are truth, love.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.43,1:49:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The nonlinear dimension, then, is what we merge into with spiritual evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.98,1:49:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As we let go, hanging on to and clutching at opinions and positionalities,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.39,1:49:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more that we open ourselves so that our life then becomes a prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.78,1:49:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, what can I do to advance myself spiritually?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.78,1:49:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it shocks me that when they ask me at the end of a lecture.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.51,1:49:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suggest you just do this and they own this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.51,1:49:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't what you do, it's what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.46,1:49:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you become that which is integrous.
