Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.82,1:50:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It sanctifies that which is integrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.72,1:50:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By being the field instead of the content of the field, then,
