Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.78,1:51:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There are thousands on the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:18.49,1:51:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we raise the level of consciousness of mankind only a couple of degrees,
