Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.52,1:51:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's our collective intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.90,1:51:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, what can I do for God?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:32.90,1:51:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for my fellow human being?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.90,1:51:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for peace?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:39.38,1:51:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, you can leave your peace science home.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.86,1:51:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.86,1:51:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it creates antagonism and conflict.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.86,1:51:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs, face shields, clubs, bloody bodies.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.94,1:51:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a political slogan, politicizing peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:56.94,1:51:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You become that.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.29,1:52:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.29,1:52:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You see from our diagram up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.35,1:52:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the field and by virtue of that which you are,
